data.description: MONTECITO GEM! LOCATION LOCATION.  Get excited about this turnkey 5 bedrooms + 2 lofts home nestled in the Otay Ranch neighborhood.  The first floor has the attached & very spacious 2 car garage, dining area, kitchen with lots of storage & living room. The second floor includes a Loft, Master bedroom & 2 secondary bedrooms & the 3rd floor has 2 more additional bedrooms with the second loft.  This beauty offers a bright open floor concept, and it features lots of upgrades, including luxury vinyl flooring, an open kitchen with granite countertops and upgraded appliances, modern bathroom vanities, a large soaking tub, and so much more! The home is located near excellent eateries, shopping, and parks!
